The '''Blue Blerd of Happiness Tavern''' was located in the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[City/Legends|city]] of [[Hweg Shul]], on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Nam Chorios/Legends|Nam Chorios]].

==History==
[[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] stayed at the Tavern during his search for [[Callista Ming]] in [[13 ABY/Legends|13 ABY]].

